messages.message: Hey i enabled this, and haven’t found any issues, but haven’t seen (or not seen) improvements either. Is there something we should use to benchmark this?
Could this issue here be related to this setting being enabled? https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C0516UPPMT3/p1701344727429259

@Lee do you mean you are still seeing verbose responses? Are you using "Extraction" mode? this pipeline doesn't apply to "Reasoning" prompts. I immediately saw improvements in my test docs using this new pipeline, so if you aren't seeing any improvement, we should take a look at your docs and see how the pipeline can be improved.
